{"tid":1007241,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"24歲美國女憂鬱症想自殺　高富帥帶遊世界讓她「爽到不想死」#bye#lny","createTime":"2019-02-03T15:35:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-04T17:29:53.000Z","uid":52127,"like":9,"dislike":99,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"8519b42b1da0581d6ea2716db49c49265a758126","tid":1007241,"uid":52127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:35:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2665/d2665103.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2665%2Fd2665103.jpg&h=4b2cd98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲海蒂3年前罹患憂鬱症，自殺「告別旅程」遇見高富帥扭轉人生。（圖／翻攝Heidy Pandora臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n網路小組／外電報導<br />\n<br />\n24歲的美國女孩海蒂潘朵拉（Heidy Pandora），臉書上有不少出遊照，個性看似陽光，但3年前她其實飽受憂鬱症所苦，曾萌生自殺念頭。自殺前，她為自己安排一趟「告別人生」的旅程，就近去了墨西哥，沒想到邂逅一位高富帥，帶她體驗有錢人的享樂生活，讓她覺得自己「值得被愛，爽得都不想死了」。<br />\n<br />\n據《每日郵報（Daily Mail）》報導，自此之後，海蒂成為伴遊女郎，陪伴有錢的陌生男子或已婚男出遊，成為她享受人生的方式。3年前，她開始在交友網站《Seeking Arrangement》上，尋找「高富帥」的網友，陪伴他們環遊世界。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2665/d2665105.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2665%2Fd2665105.jpg&h=8d43d00a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲海蒂遇見高富帥後，靠與他們出遊，玩遍各國。（圖／翻攝Heidy Pandora臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n跨出家鄉佛羅里達，海蒂去了杜拜、摩洛哥、夏威夷、泰國等20個國家，陪伴寂寞的人們旅行，欣賞世界美景，體驗「上流社會」人生，還被無微不至的照顧。海蒂表示：「這是我活著的動力。」雖然憂鬱症沒被完全治癒，但現在的她心理狀態比3年前好很多。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2665/d2665104.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2665%2Fd2665104.jpg&h=41e9d094&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲海蒂認為體驗上流社會人生，是她活著的動力。（圖／翻攝Heidy Pandora臉書）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n雖然海蒂靠著與有錢人出遊，療癒身心，但如此作法引來網友正反兩極的評價，不過她本人說：「其他人怎麼想，我管不著。」對她來說，一場場「甜蜜的冒險」，是把她從地獄邊緣救回來的方式。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/2665/d2665106.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F2665%2Fd2665106.jpg&h=03ccd7e9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲海蒂認為網友怎麼想不重要，對她來說這些是精神支柱。（圖／翻攝Heidy Pandora臉書）"},{"pid":"968774e6d578e6774133e989f0270dd29007c4bc","tid":1007241,"uid":1139,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:36:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e5c110a1e154593e1372a390a661365900ab2def","tid":1007241,"uid":106482,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:37:17.000Z","msg":"G"},{"pid":"d302761a6a351effd29b282ea4f653270262428d","tid":1007241,"uid":693,"like":65,"dislike":2,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"走左去做高級G<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32e4ba6a7351c7a50861bbd07c6a42880ad2b96e","tid":1007241,"uid":11254,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:38:03.000Z","msg":"講咁多 姐係做G啦"},{"pid":"89242ecd6f1a620f056c3b58f71fe035d3fc9599","tid":1007241,"uid":52127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:38:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PpU134sQSeY?t=39\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPpU134sQSeY%3Ft%3D39&d=GmsUkepvXW4IpX0DHJvToGhNlLB%2BLbsdBqu6cuXqlDc%3D&h=6a2d3848\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PpU134sQSeY?t=39</a>"},{"pid":"4de0a7f8613232a49d21dfaee37d9010b5b61528","tid":1007241,"uid":39777,"like":113,"dislike":1,"score":112,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:38:15.000Z","msg":"證明有錢可以治抑鬱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e44f7f8dc650bc4defff05c3e42d15033d9ce76f","tid":1007241,"uid":63303,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:39:00.000Z","msg":"伴遊=<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61d81f79abf2449cbc11c029624ea2cd7f5f9913","tid":1007241,"uid":24696,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-03T15:39:11.000Z","msg":"值得被做愛，爽得都不想死了"},{"pid":"8625e7f305808